### ========================================
### AyniPay API — Documentación
### ========================================
### Swagger UI: http://localhost:3000/api
### Postman/REST Client: VS Code extension
### ========================================

### Variables globales
@baseUrl = https://dot-revealable-telescopically.ngrok-free.dev/
@token = <PEGAR_TOKEN_AQUI>



### ========================================
### AUTH — Público (sin token)
### ========================================

### 1. Registrar usuario (estudiante)
POST {{baseUrl}}/user/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre": "María García",
  "correo": "maria@example.com",
  "password": "123456",
  "telefono": "555-0101",
  "tipo_usuario": "estudiante"
}

### 2. Registrar usuario (comercio)
POST {{baseUrl}}/user/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre": "Tacos El Güero",
  "correo": "tacos@example.com",
  "password": "123456",
  "tipo_usuario": "comercio"
}


### 4. Login — Recibes JWT (úsalo en @token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/user/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "correo": "maria@example.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

### Ejemplo de respuesta login:
### {
###   "access_token": "eyJhbGci...",
###   "usuario": {
###     "id_usuario": "uuid",
###     "nombre": "María García",
###     "correo": "maria@example.com",
###     "tipo_usuario": "estudiante",
###     "estado": "activo"
###   }
### }
### ========================================



### ========================================
### USER — Protegido (requiere @token)
### ========================================

### 5. Mi perfil (del token JWT)
GET {{baseUrl}}/user/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. Listar todos los usuarios
GET {{baseUrl}}/user
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7. Obtener usuario por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/user/<UUID_DEL_USUARIO>
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8. Actualizar usuario
PUT {{baseUrl}}/user/<UUID_DEL_USUARIO>
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre": "María Actualizada",
  "telefono": "555-0999"
}

### 9. Actualizar password
PUT {{baseUrl}}/user/<UUID_DEL_USUARIO>
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "password": "nueva_contraseña"
}

### 10. Eliminar usuario (soft delete)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/user/<UUID_DEL_USUARIO>
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
### ========================================



### ========================================
### NOTAS
### ========================================
### - Los campos 'estudiante', 'comercio', 'entidad' en tipo_usuario
### - JWT expira en 7 días
### - La contraseña se hashea con bcrypt
### - Los campos nuevos (wallet_address, kyc_sbt_hash) se agregan al actualizar
### - Swagger: http://localhost:3000/api para probar endpoints visualmente